<H3> <TI>   Bossi Chooses Maroni for Government </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bossi Chooses Maroni for Government </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3103190494 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1700 GMT 
31 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3103190494 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>
<F P=105>  Italian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] "The Northern League is the leading political force 
in the country, and especially in the Chamber of Deputies. So 
we must act as if we already had an objectively effective 
mandate from the president, who must give the mandate to form a 
