<F P=102>   TA0404132994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0404132994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] Husamettin Cindoruk, Turkish Grand National 
Assembly [TGNA] speaker, has left for Bulgaria as the official 
guest of the Bulgarian National Assembly Speaker Georgi Yordanov 
[name and title as received]. 
  In a statement he made prior to his departure at Istanbul's 
