<H3> <TI>   Fourteen `Terrorists' Killed, 24 Captured in Southeast </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fourteen `Terrorists' Killed, 24 Captured in Southeast </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0404125794 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0404125794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] Fourteen terrorists have been killed near Bingol's 
Dallitepe region and Diyarbakir's Silvan District following 
clashes with the security forces. 
  A terrorist in Sirnak was captured alive after the bomb he 
was trying to place in a school exploded in his hands. 
  In Bitlis Province and Tatvan and Ahlat Districts, 24 
persons 
were captured on charges of cooperating with the terrorist 
organization. 

</TEXT>

