<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Scalfaro Congratulates Maltese President on Election </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0504152094 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1338 GMT 5 
Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0504152094 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


